item.title: merge tank shooter
item.author: yeniuzaiyc@gmail.com (Bingjue123)
item.description: Explore the world of merging tanks and embark on a new era of strategic battles! Game Overview In this captivating strategy game, you will play as a tank commander, merging identical tanks to upgrade into a more advanced tank. Each tank possesses unique skills and combat power. You’ll need to employ flexible strategies on the battlefield, directing your tank army to defeat the enemy. Game Features Merge to Upgrade: By merging two of the same tanks, you will obtain a higher-level, more powerful tank.

item.title: Mind Jigsaw Puzzle
item.author: yeniuzaiyc@gmail.com (Bingjue123)
item.description: Experience a unique puzzle game with hexagonal pieces! Enjoy the satisfaction of colorful, perfect fits as challenges grow! Game Overview Challenge your puzzle-solving abilities with a fresh take on the classic dissection game! Our unique hexagonal pieces promise a brain-teasing, addictive puzzle experience. Revel in the satisfaction of seeing pieces perfectly falling into place, painting the board with vibrant colors. As you fill the gaps and grow your skills, the challenges intensify.
